import React from 'react';
import { FaBars } from 'react-icons/fa';
import { Nav, NavbarContainer, NavLogo, MobileIcon, NavMenu, NavItem, NavLinks, NavBtn, NavBtnLink } from './NavbarElements';

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Nav>
        <NavbarContainer>
          <NavLogo to='/'>GYM</NavLogo>
          <MobileIcon>
            <FaBars />
          </MobileIcon>
          <NavMenu>
            <NavItem>
              <NavLinks to='acasa'>Acasa</NavLinks>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem>
              <NavLinks to='antrenamente'>Antrenamente</NavLinks>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem>
              <NavLinks to='despre'>Despre</NavLinks>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem>
              <NavLinks to='Button4'>Button4</NavLinks>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem>
              <NavLinks to='Button5'>Button5</NavLinks>
            </NavItem>
          </NavMenu>
          <NavBtn>
            <NavBtnLink to='/signup'>Sign Up</NavBtnLink>
          </NavBtn>
        </NavbarContainer>
      </Nav>
    </>
  );
};

export default Navbar;
